transform_def.name: designed20
transform_def.string: let r = 1 / length(p_in) s = log(abs(length(p_in) * (p_in.x + p_in.y))) * log(abs(length(p_in) * (p_in.x - p_in.y))) * (p_in.x / p_in.y) / pi() t = (sin(p_in.x * sin(length(p_in) / twopi() + cos(p_in.y + twopi()))) * s) / fourpi() u = tan(p_in.x) v = tan(p_in.y) z = (if s > t then u else v) / (twopi() * fmod(length(p_in * (s / twopi())), halfpi() / length(p_in))) / fourpi() con1 = abs(z) < r con2 = abs(z) > r in (if if fill > 0.0 then con1 else con2 then p_in else vec2(0.0)) * weight
